#  installation as part of the `base` package — it's a SIMPLE,
#  RECORD-BASED, GNU getopt-style API written by Sven Panne in 2001
#  for the Haskell standard library.  Used by arbtt, GHC itself
#  (`ghc` driver uses GetOpt internally), `cabal-install`, `runghc`,
#  many academic/research Haskell tools, and most Haskell tools that
#  prefer a minimal-dependency approach (zero external libraries
#  required — ships with base).
